				<h3>The Food Lab: Fresh Ricotta in Five Minutes or Less</h3>
			
				<p class="byline">Posted by <a href="http://www.seriouseats.com/user/profile/GoodEaterKenji">J. Kenji Lopez-Alt</a>, February 19, 2010 at  7:30 AM</p>     
			

				     
